posts.subject: Youtube keeps shoa-ing imporant vids
posts.body:
==ITT we keep thoughtcrime alive==

I've increasingly been drip-feeding my friends redpills, and I find myself needing to send them a video or two for reference. 

Disturbingly, these videos have a trend of (((disappearing))). Most recently, I went to go find the Youtube video of some guy going undercover and interviewing a bunch of fags about their sexual history. The video is about 30 minutes long, and he goes to multiple bars and they talk about how they were mostly abused. I think it was fairly popular and I'm sure some of you autists remember it.

This is the original link (not that it matters): https://www. youtube.com/watch?v=sTYvTj8Ss6g

Does anyone have a saved or archived version?

Additionally, I went to find a video about some fake holocaust survivor being interviewed by a mainstream outlet. It's pretty old, and I remember him saying "It was true to me" or something like that. Any source on this would be appreciated.


Also, I figure ITT we ask fellow anons for help located similarly disappearing content. I'm sure this will only happen more frequently as time passes.

I have been following a mostly carnivore diet lately.
